Business Brief -- United Technologies Corp.:
   Judge Declines to Dismiss
   Lawsuit Alleging Bribery
The suit was filed by Thomas F. Dooley, an employee of
United Technologies' Sikorsky Aircraft unit. It names 21
defendants, including United Technologies Chairman Robert F.
Daniell. The company has maintained that the suit is "without
merit," and yesterday a spokesman said the company is
"prepared to proceed now that the Judge has ruled."